urdu transliteration text:
Zuljana ay zuljana, mera bacha hai(n) kahan
Zuljana O Zuljana,
@HujjatELC

tere mathe pe khun hai kiska, rang khu(n) ye tere sawaar ka tha, hai mere shir ki mehek usme, kampta hai alam se dil mera, bol khamosh hai kyu(n), tere asu(n) hai rawaa, mera bacha hai(n) kahaa(n)
My heart is completely broken now,
@HujjatELC

kaise soyegi ladli uski, jisko sine pa neend aati thi, jisne roka tha tujhko jaate huwe, kya kahega agar wo puchhegi, samna uska na kar, roke dedegi wo jaa(n), mera bacha hai(n) kahaa(n)
Don’t face her
@HujjatELC
